item.title: Need help with launching a 562
item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

If you have recently downloaded it and testing it then it might have some code/files missing or be part of an anti-theft process. I recommend that if you have added something recently that you take it out and try it again. Message me for help over Teamviewer.
